requires:
  weather resistant loud speaker
  microcontroller
  button panel
  power regulation
  DAC MAX98357A
  case
  sdcard slot
  lcd
  
  
Goal:
  Load an SD card with WAV files then using the buttons select the specific sound to play and have it play on the loud speaker. 
  
features:
  Unlimited # of possibles sounds
  set favorites to buttons
  external button input
  volume control
  
